Text: Does anyone have the Boundless LD 18-22 available? I see torrents for LD 1-17, and individual copies of 23-24-25, but there's that missing gap. Thanks!
quoting blackcanary a few weeks ago: "For those wondering, 2Radbits is in the process of scanning Lady Death #18-22 (there are many variant covers). Once they're scanned, they'll be uploaded. :) "
